嘿 老兄
Hey, man.

148
00:14:25,114 --> 00:14:26,615
很高兴见到你
It's good to see you.

149
00:14:28,159 --> 00:14:30,035
他们到阿拉斯加了吗
Did they make it to Alaska?

150
00:14:30,036 --> 00:14:31,286
