- Four months - Four months?

162
00:14:57,730 --> 00:15:00,190
他从一个变态手中救了他老婆
He saved his wife from a fucking psychopath.

163
00:15:00,191 --> 00:15:03,568
而卢克是对加拿大公民实施犯罪的难民
And Luke's a refugee who committed a crime against a Canadian citizen.

164
00:15:03,569 --> 00:15:05,362
